channel.title: Added objects appearing in weird places
channel.description:
So, as the title says, the objects i added are duplicating. For example, i added portal at X2824 Y3808 and ice throne at X2824 Y3809. They also appeared at X3080 Y3552 and X3080 Y3553. Could someone help me remove the unwanted objects?
Ty. :)

item.title: Added objects appearing in weird places
item.dc:creator: @Jellybean732 Jellybean732
item.description:
@Jellybean732 wrote:

Add this void public void deletethatobject(int objectX, int objectY) { ReplaceObject2(objectX, objectY, 6951, -1, 10); }

then set it out like this deletethatobject(XCoord, YCoord); underneath the void.
